This is MARBLE. If we can't help find her a home, she will have to go to a shelter. She's a lovable, beautiful, sweet OLDER kitty. She is between 8 and 9 years old and chances are if she ends up at a shelter,  they won't give her much of a chance.  She's fixed and has all her shots. Her family can't keep her and asked us to help find her a home. Her family is 💔 that they can't keep her.  She deserves a happy, warm home with a new loving family, not having her life cut short after being shoved into a cold cage, scared, alone and away from the family she loved. PLEASE SHARE THIS  and if you or someone you know can help, please DM ME ASAP.
*Rescues aren't even taking kittens right now, much less an older cat.
*Please remember that even though she's 8 or 9 yrs old, a pet can still be a 20+ year total commitment, so pls keep that in mind. 
*Please share/repost. ❤️
